             leptospirosis with serological testing or PCR&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  onset of symptoms within 21 days&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  participant benefits of health insurance&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  participant's refusal, or refusal from his relatives in case of major incapacity of&#xD;
             the eligible participant precluding expression of his will (coma, stay in intensive&#xD;
